Smasher Mix
Smasher Mix is funny cool popular game for all family. During years many millions of families using this time wasting app downloading it from Apple App Store. The game is highly popular in Russia and Mexico. Gameplay is very easy - just tap on running insects and have points . Android version of game is new released and now android users have chance to play ! Just install , tap and enjoy !!!
