Muzzle Puzzle
Muzzle puzzle is very old Apple App Store puzzle game for all family. There is 3 packs to play - easy , normal and hard. Younger users can use easy pack , a middle level users can use normal pack and only professional can win hard level. Solving puzzles you can also enjoy funny cute monsters and lovely music . Time to enjoy :)
