ABOUT US
Sgames llc is mobile game publisher based in Armenia started from 2016. Our games are made for all ages. We make casual games, which are popular in all over the world. Balls was in top ranks on Russian App Store during years. Smasher Mix are more loved in Mexico and Muzzle Puzzle are played more in Europe. We make games making happy more than 10 millions users everywhere. Sgames - Time to Play !